Two top of the range sports cars have been stolen after burglars broke into a house and stole the keys.

A dark-blue Aston Martin DB7 and a black Porsche Cayenne were taken from the driveway of a house in North Road, Bathwick, Bath.

Burglars stole the keys to the cars, which police described as 'distinctive', from the property between midnight and 8.30am today.

